h4. Actor:
Administrator,Software Engineer,SQA.

h4. Description:
This is the landing page of "Active Backlog" with input form on top and grid view at the bottom.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Project Track|guide:_ShowProjectTrackPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* "Project" sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click "Active" link.
* Show Landing Page of *Active Backlog*.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Show Active Backlog" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Show blank input form to [Create "Backlog"|guide:CreatePtBacklogActionService].
* [List of all "Backlog"|guide:ListPtBacklogActionService].

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show *Backlog* information in grid view.
** Reset input form on top to create new *Backlog*.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

h4. Related Usecase:
* [Cancel|common Usecases].

